VOTABLE.DESCRIPTION: DASCH: Digital Access to a Sky Century @ Harvard Harvard College Observatory astronomical plate photometry data http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/

FIELD.name: ExposureDate
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Geocentric Julian date of plate or Heliocentric Julian date of an image http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/database.php#heliocentric

FIELD.name: magcal_local_rms
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Error of the locally corrected magnitude. http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/database.php#magcallocalrms

FIELD.name: THETA_J2000
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Image angle in degrees East of North. See sextractor manual.

FIELD.name: Plate
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: HCO plate designation (series and number within series) http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/database.php#plateSelection

FIELD.name: versionId
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Index into the photometry version table for GSC2.3.2 stars

FIELD.name: timeAccuracy
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Accuracy of logbook time in days http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/database.php#timeAccuracy_ext

FIELD.name: AFLAGSBits
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Listing of bits set in the photometry warning flags http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/database.php#AFLAGS_ext

FIELD.name: BFLAGSBits
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Listing of bits set in the photometry processing flags http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/database.php#BFLAGS_ext

FIELD.name: qualitybits
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Listing of bits set in plate quality flags http://dasch.rc.fas.harvard.edu/database.php#quality_ext
